flowchart LR
  Client[Authenticated client] --> Controller[DashboardController]
  Controller --> Service[DashboardService]
  Service --> Query[Build user-scoped dashboard query]
  Query --> Repository[DashboardRepository]
  Repository --> Aggregate[Prisma aggregate count groupBy]
  Repository --> RawSQL[Parameterized date_trunc SQL]
  Repository --> Recent[Recent transaction select]
  Aggregate --> Database[(PostgreSQL)]
  RawSQL --> Database
  Recent --> Database
  Database --> Repository
  Repository --> Mapper[DashboardMapper]
  Mapper --> Service
  Service --> Envelope[ApiResponseInterceptor]
  Envelope --> Client

  Query -. filters .-> Filters[startDate endDate month year type categoryId groupBy limit cursor]
